{"tid":488563,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"罩杯咖啡店　加奶不加價","createTime":"2017-12-03T23:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T07:57:18.000Z","uid":81228,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"61c9f903295c9e0cf0e4eea458f27b14b5f30ebf","tid":488563,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T23:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.chinapress.com.my/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/20171202fb82d_noresize.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinapress.com.my%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F20171202fb82d_noresize.jpg&h=7b276645&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.chinapress.com.my/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/20171202fb82e_noresize.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinapress.com.my%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F20171202fb82e_noresize.jpg&h=fc81ad06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近日通訊軟體《LINE》流傳兩張穿著輕涼的咖啡店店員照片，一度被誤傳是台南市某咖啡廳，導致該店電話被打爆、民眾詢問不斷。翻攝臉書<br />\n<br />\n濃醇香！近日通訊軟體《LINE》流傳兩張穿著輕涼的咖啡店店員照片，一度被誤傳是台南市某咖啡廳，導致該店電話被打爆、民眾詢問不斷，為了闢謠，這家咖啡廳日前特別在《臉書》粉絲專頁po文澄清，表示該照片店名、地址均為誤植，原圖拍攝地點應是泰國知名的辣妹咖啡餐廳「C罩杯咖啡」（CUP C Cafe House），有網友循線搜索找出幾張C罩杯咖啡店內實拍照片，證實店員果然個個胸如店名、乳量驚人，「什麼C罩杯！這是我見過最大杯的了！」<br />\n<br />\n2013年開幕的「C罩杯咖啡」，店內一大特色就是店員每個都是經過老闆精挑細選的辣妹，除了上圍至少必須符合店名要求之外，顏值也必須要有一定水準，但如果以為這家咖啡店「掛羊頭賣狗肉」就大錯特錯了，根據曾經造訪過此地的泰國網友表示，「C罩杯咖啡」的咖啡非常正統、餐點也不錯吃，店員態度友善、氣氛很好，是一個適合闔家大小假日外出聚餐的好所在，很多男客常常店一開門就來報到，坐到晚上9點結束營業才離開，「這家店的咖啡真的會讓人不想回家啊！」（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171130/640_de6479bcb35a26c3a33c87369dfd86c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171130%2F640_de6479bcb35a26c3a33c87369dfd86c3.jpg&h=0e65b149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原圖拍攝地點應是泰國知名的辣妹咖啡餐廳「C罩杯咖啡」（CUP C Cafe House）。翻攝臉書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171130/640_12b9a175a987430c95ac631da98a7687.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171130%2F640_12b9a175a987430c95ac631da98a7687.jpg&h=aa2cc601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n店內一大特色就是店員每個都是經過老闆精挑細選的辣妹，除了上圍至少必須符合店名要求之外，顏值也必須要有一定水準。翻攝臉書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171130/640_e979fdb4be691ef198b098f4a650a8fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171130%2F640_e979fdb4be691ef198b098f4a650a8fa.jpg&h=acca197e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據曾經造訪過此地的泰國網友表示，「C罩杯咖啡」的咖啡非常正統。翻攝臉書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171130/640_54a275a0dfefa20e6825cfdd9e1ffc11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171130%2F640_54a275a0dfefa20e6825cfdd9e1ffc11.jpg&h=b06f392d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n餐點也不錯吃。翻攝臉書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171130/640_8245d0ea6e332f5cca63e946acad4bff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171130%2F640_8245d0ea6e332f5cca63e946acad4bff.jpg&h=6358b9ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n店員態度友善。翻攝臉書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171130/640_632d85500b4120e826c1815285a4d677.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171130%2F640_632d85500b4120e826c1815285a4d677.jpg&h=d663f7cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n店內氣氛很好。翻攝臉書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171130/640_f5984d1be8e2c12be8c674509dac670f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171130%2F640_f5984d1be8e2c12be8c674509dac670f.jpg&h=9414ea71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是一個適合闔家大小假日外出聚餐的好所在。翻攝臉書<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20171130/640_bd32f8c55e5375e669f7ce786d5f1b44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20171130%2F640_bd32f8c55e5375e669f7ce786d5f1b44.jpg&h=0d3c7a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n很多男客常常店一開門就來報到，坐到晚上9點結束營業才離開。翻攝臉書<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171130/1251016/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171130%2F1251016%2F&d=Sz9Z6jrxRbOMhRsQ2l3tXBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8880bd4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20171130%2F1251016%2F&h=ef3d4c63\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20171130/1251016/</a><br />\n記者郭彥廷、李世泓／台南報導<br />\n<br />\n前陣子網路上瘋傳一系列泰國某間餐廳，有火辣C罩杯女店員為大家服務，網友誤認這家咖啡館在台南，於是蜂擁朝聖，但結果卻是相當失望。老闆為了補償客人，週末真的找來多位辣妹擔任一日店員，果然讓許多男顧客回流。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/12/02/1160892-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F1160892-XXL.jpg&h=b4d707ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲台南某咖啡店邀請辣妹當一日店員。<br />\n<br />\n咖啡店裡好幾名女員工穿著細肩帶、純白小可愛，露出性感小蠻腰又穿著火辣熱褲，細心幫客人介紹咖啡，讓來店消費的顧客賓至如歸。來店男顧客：「賞心悅目，服務非常的好。」來店男顧客：「就看到網路po文，所以就過來了。」<br />\n<br />\n不少客人因為火辣女店員慕名而來，而店家為什麼會舉辦辣妹女店員活動，起因都是因為這幾張照片。咖啡店裡，女員工穿著細肩帶露出大片美背，又或是微微彎腰，性感的S曲線加上姣好身材讓顧客眼睛大吃冰淇淋，到底什麼店的員工這麼火辣？<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/12/02/1160891-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F1160891-XXL.jpg&h=c349d55e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲台灣版與泰國版的正妹店員各有千秋。（圖／翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n原來是泰國的一間餐廳，但在網路瘋傳讓人誤以為在台南，讓這間咖啡店生意暴增，之前因為不少消費者特地到店裡想一睹辣妹風采，卻都敗興而歸，所以店家特地舉辦這次活動。咖啡廳業者蘇先生：「來消費，我們決定說今天辦一個活動，來回饋這些朋友跟觀眾。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2017/12/02/1160955-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2017%2F12%2F02%2F1160955-XXL.jpg&h=c7fab6ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲男客人認為正妹店員不僅服務好，更賞心悅目。"},{"pid":"f7cc191617992ede4557e34385743593aa43a2c2","tid":488563,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T23:50:52.000Z","msg":"實際來比一比，台灣店員外形甜美穿著短版小可愛，露出性感小蠻腰；泰國版的戴著黑框眼鏡，走文青風衣樣加上削肩小可愛，擁有傲人上圍，各有千秋。店家邀請辣妹擔任一日服務生，還原相片場景，忠實顧客這次終於沒有失望而歸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=321450\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D321450&d=Sz9Z6jrxRbOMhRsQ2l3tXBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=0eca42f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D321450&h=45126988\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=321450</a>"},{"pid":"9f3a2e8be9b95afd7e1d6049f29d2a8720dc2319","tid":488563,"uid":64318,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T23:52:01.000Z","msg":"男黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1365e0cb6fe554ebc65d42a774eb78d6a56d1130","tid":488563,"uid":99582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T02:36:36.000Z","msg":"泰妹真係好正"},{"pid":"2de28d6802536a48e3c56341755c99031f3ba119","tid":488563,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T02:41:31.000Z","msg":"店員好相遇"},{"pid":"06db34afbe5186a2d9fd235ccc6eb7991ed152df","tid":488563,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T03:53:11.000Z","msg":"香港可以搞大把a 級店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a74a92444899b053d2d52625d47a55b16bfd676","tid":488563,"uid":76403,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T05:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港可以搞大把a 級店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人哋就掛名C級實際C~E<br />\n香港就掛名A級實際A～AAA<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2156f65be716b9a92c559645a950e80cc190ed3e","tid":488563,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港可以搞大把a 級店<img src=\"/assets/